<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6496060>
    dc:description "Fig. 19. Postero-ventral part of internal RV in Siamopsis spp., showing a smooth inner list and a few tiny tubercle-like structures beneath the inner list. A. S. renateae gen. et sp. nov. B. S. conspecta gen. et sp. nov. C. S. suttajit gen. et sp. nov. D. S. khoratensis gen. et sp. nov. E. S. planitia gen. et sp. nov. Scale bar: 100 μm. Arrows indicate tiny tubercle-like structures under postero-ventral inner list." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6496060/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6496062>
    dc:description "Fig. 20. Sampling localities of species of Siamopsis gen. nov. (for information on locality numbers, see the text)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6496062/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6496052>
    dc:description "Fig. 15. Siamopsis planitia gen. et sp. nov., ♀. A. CpL (MSU-ZOC.209). B. LVi (MSU-ZOC.207). C. RVi (idem). D. Valve surface of CpL (MSU-ZOC.209). E. Postero-dorsal part of LVi (MSU-ZOC.207). F. Postero-dorsal part of RVi (idem). Scale bar: A–C = 200 μm; D = 64 μm; E–F = 85 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6496052/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6496054>
    dc:description "Fig. 16. Siamopsis planitia gen. et sp. nov., ♀ (MSU-ZOC.207). A. A1. B. A2. C. Md coxa. Scale bar: 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6496054/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6496056>
    dc:description "Fig. 17. Siamopsis planitia gen. et sp. nov., ♀ (MSU-ZOC.207). A. Md palp. B. Mx1. C. T1, apical setae on protopodite. D. T1. Scale bars: 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6496056/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6496058>
    dc:description "Fig. 18. Siamopsis planitia gen. et sp. nov., ♀ (MSU-ZOC.207). A. T2. B. T3. C. CR. Scale bars: 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6496058/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

